      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your feelings of emptiness and disconnection are valid, but they don't mean you have to stay in this shell. Sometimes stepping away from the piano and letting go of the need to feel everything all at once can help you find a new rhythm. It's okay to take it slow and see if a different kind of connection emerges, even if it feels small right now.",
      "source": "target",
